57E"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "2245538989150890", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572954_2245538992484223_8598079660398496648_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IzYgB-1f7HgQ7kNvgFDccW_&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBz857WeMrsfrb1bB97PhL_KulCb59Bpj7HoiLBNl1svg&oe=673472BC"}, {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "2673319909520060", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982510_2673319912853393_2503569918825159240_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YyEUQ0G9m0cQ7kNvgHLJDUr&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB0z0TxvQd4hPPBLeElbi7FoSKvha4g-0tn9eH_4CP-sg&oe=6734A7D7"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Drum Circle Cover Art (2560 x 1440 px) (1).png", "id": "1161447404916858", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982625_1161447408250191_2650284731583729103_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=q9U06BzK-ooQ7kNvgEDoI7T&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlPjY7FVuw5uYslfJ5cKTL07PjvYDlyP0RG0_aJG579A&oe=67348B02"}, "display_name": "Drum Circle", "keywords": ["Drum", "Music", "Piano", "Jam", "Songs"], "long_description": "Unleash your inner musician with *Drum Circle*! Step into a vibrant virtual world where you can play a variety of instruments using just your hands. Whether you're grooving on the conga drums, tapping out rhythms on the bongos, creating melodies on a keyboard, or shaking maracas to the beat, *Drum Circle* brings the joy of music-making to life in immersive VR.\n\n**Features:**\n- Play a range of instruments: congas, bongos, keyboards, and maracas!\n- Play along with *music tracks* or create your own rhythms and melodies\n- Intuitive hand-tracking lets you perform naturally without controllers\n- Use passthrough to enhance real-world collaboration and participate in live music sessions\n\nGet ready to feel the rhythm, unleash your creativity, and make music 